- Reproduction in *Paramecium*:
    - *Binary fission*: Micronucleus divides mitotically; macronucleus amitotically.
    - *Conjugation*: Exchange of micronuclear material between two individuals (sexual).
    - *Autogamy*: Self-fertilization.

#figure(
  image(images.at("figure-11-27").path, width: 60%),
